column1: % N-Back Matches Not Zapped but Grabbed - Ignored
% N-Back Non-Matches Not Zapped but Grabbed - Pickups
% Score - Player points earned in level
% Total Marbles - Levels left in the random pool for the scheduler
% NBackLevelC - Sound Only  scheduler skill level
% NBackLevelD - All Signals scheduler skill level
% Holdout OffsetA - Offset to Color/Sound skill level in scheduler
% Holdout OffsetB - Offset to Shape/Sound skill level in scheduler
% Holdout OffsetD - Offset to All Signals skill level in scheduler
% Holdout LevelA - Represents number of succeed levels in holdout A in scheduler
% Holdout LevelB - Represents number of succeed levels in holdout B in scheduler
% Holdout LevelD - Represents number of succeed levels in holdout D in scheduler
% SpeedA - Scheduler recommended speed for Color/Sound
% SpeedB - Scheduler recommended speed for Shape/Sound
% SpeedC - Scheduler recommended speed for Sound Only
% SpeedD - Scheduler recommended speed for All Signals
% SpeedE - Scheduler recommended speed for Recess
% Sync Data To Server - Settings that lets user to sync log data to server
% Max Vel - Controller Settings for maximum angular spin
% Min Vel Stopper - Controller Settings for minimum velocity to force stop in free motion
% Damping Decay Free - Controller Settings for a multiplier to slow down in free motion
% Damping Decay Stop - Controller Settings for a multiplier to slow down by held down input
% Damping Drop Free - Controller Settings for a linear slow down in free motion
% Damping Drop Stop - Controller Settings for a linear slow down by held down input
% Inverted - Controller Settings to invert direction
% fuelEnabled - Study Settings to enable fuel usage
% holdoutEnabled - Study Settings to enable holdout
% initialVelocity - Study Settings to initialize starting speed
% manRecessEnabled - Study Settings to enable mandatory recess
% manRecessLevelLimit - Study Settings to set the number of levels before mandatory recess
% newNavEnabled - Study Settings to enable senior navigation
% newNavIncrement - Study Settings to set senior navigation progression
% indRecessEnabled - Study Settings to enable independent recess
% indRecessIncrement - Study Settings to set independent recess increment
% holdoutdelayEnabled - Study Settings to enable delayed holdout
% holdoutdelayNumber - Study Settings to set holdout delay memory level
% newSounds - Study Settings to use new sounds
% enableSettingsPasscode - Study Settings to enable Settings Passcode
% sessionStartTime - Study Settings to set min session length in mins
% sessionEndTime - Study Settings to set max session length in mins
% numOfSessions - Study Settings to set number of sessions
% sessionScreenEnabled - Study Settings to enable the SessionID screen
% enableIndRecessFixed - Study Settings to enable fixed Navigation for Independent Recess Levels
% holdoutMin - Study Settings for min holdout intensity
% holdoutMax - Study Settings for max holdout intensity
% holdoutLowerBoundTime - Study Settings for in-level lowerbound time holdout
% holdoutUpperBoundMinTime - Study Settings for in-level upperbound min time holdout
% holdoutUpperBoundMaxTime - Study Settings for in-level upperbound max time holdout
% holdoutSteps - Study Settings for holdout steps
% soundOnlyEnabled - Study Settings for marble generation for Sound Only
% holdoutOnlyEnabled - Study Settings for holdout marble only generation
